---
import Scribble2 from "../Scribble2.astro";
---

<div class="grid place-content-center p-32">
  <section id="about" class="w-full max-w-7xl flex flex-col items-center gap-5">
    <div class="relative w-full max-w-[600px] h-[450px] mb-8">
      <div class="absolute top-[58%] left-[65%] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rotate-[15deg] w-[290px] h-[300px] border border-gray-300 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-[#fafafa] rounded-[17px] shadow-[inset_0px_-3.51px_0.35px_0px_rgba(188,188,188,0.3)] overflow-hidden p-3">
        <img
          src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/MzLHugGNcS9QpzwIXYLsrWiWSU.png"
          alt="Man working on laptop"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-[11px]"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute top-[41%] left-[35%] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -rotate-[15deg] w-[290px] h-[300px] border border-gray-300 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-[#fafafa] rounded-[17px] shadow-[inset_0px_-3.51px_0.35px_0px_rgba(188,188,188,0.3)] overflow-hidden p-3">
        <img
          src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/GwacDOLnwOUtjFiLQUmSywY0mjw.png"
          alt="Man portrait"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-[11px]"
        />
      </div>
      <svg class="absolute top-[14%] left-[2.5%] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2" width="60" height="75" viewBox="0 0 56 70">
        <path
          d="M 29.185 3.359 C 27.75 16.033 20.505 41.38 3 41.38 M 29.185 3 C 30.62 11.13 37.865 27.391 55.37 27.391 C 37.865 27.391 30.62 55.131 29.185 69 C 27.75 59.913 20.505 41.74 3 41.74"
          stroke="rgb(255,189,46)"
          stroke-width="5"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          fill="transparent"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center max-w-[710px]">
      <h2 class="text-[72px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[1.2em]">Reserved,</h2>
      <div class="relative">
        <h2 class="text-[72px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[1.2em]">But Far From Ordinary!</h2>
        <Scribble2 />
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl leading-[1.6em] tracking-[-0.01em] mt-8">
        Hailing from Canada and thriving in the heart of LA, I've spent the last 7
        years partnering with visionary founders and VC-backed startups to craft
        brands, websites, apps, and marketing that leave a lasting impression.<br />
        <br />My mission? To transform big ideas into compelling digital
        experiences that captivate users, elevate products, and catch the eyes of
        investors. Together, we don't just tell stories â€“ we create moments that
        make your brand unforgettable.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>